{"id":70,"title":"问：常见的排序算法有哪些？它们的时间复杂度和稳定性如何？","slug":"问：常见的排序算法有哪些？它们的时间复杂度和稳定性如何？-1766595056","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：常见排序算法包括冒泡排序、选择排序、插入排序、归并排序、快速排序、堆排序等。它们的平均时间复杂度各不相同：冒泡、选择、插入排序为 O(n^2)，归并和堆排序为 O(n log n)，快速排序平均也是 O(n log n)（最坏情况O(n^2)）。其中，冒泡、插入、归并排序是稳定**的（不改变值相等元素的相对顺序），选择、快速、堆排序则是**不稳定**的。一般实际应用中快速排序由于平均性能优秀而被广泛使用，而当对稳定性有要求时会选用归并排序等稳定算法。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:56.538719+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:56.538719+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-80ea-a044-cee3c5c6970b","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":70,"blog_post_id":70,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.613171+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.613171+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:56.538719+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:56.538719+08:00"}